# This is a PUBLIC repo. Never commit PII or company info.

# Private Claude Code data lives as real files under ~/.claude (memory,
# commands, CLAUDE.md, credentials) and is intentionally NOT stored here.
# Only config/claude/settings.json is tracked. These globs are defense-in-depth
# in case any private Claude data ever lands in the working tree.
**/.claude/
**/.credentials.json
config/claude/memory/
config/claude/commands/
config/claude/CLAUDE.md

# Persona company build script (never publish)
packages/from-source/persona_rl.sh
